data.description: Beautiful Single-Family Home located at Regency Cove South of Coral Lakes Community. Lovely open floor plan overlooking a sprawling garden view from covered screened patio. This spacious 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 2 car garage home features an open eat-in-kitchen overlooking family room. Ceramic tile thru-out living areas. Stainless-steel appliances; totally updated kitchen and bathrooms. Coral Lakes is a most popular community with many amenities, newly renovated clubhouse. theatre, cafe, tennis and pickle ball courts with 2 pros, gym, indoor & outdoor pools. This senior community is like living in a resort. Owners want offers!!!
